NAFLD and the Gut-Liver Axis: Exploring an Undernutrition Perspective.
Here, we present undernutrition conditions with fatty liver features, including kwashiorkor and micronutrient deficiency (MND). We then review the gut microbiota-liver axis, highlighting key pathways linked to NAFLD progression within both overnutrition and undernutrition. To conclude, we identify challenges and collaborative possibilities of emerging multiomic research addressing the pathology and treatment of undernourished NAFLD.
